ine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8695638126355746e-16, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The unprecedented decision\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 292}, {\"ngram\": \"a 6-kilometer (3.7-mile) stretch\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 332}, {\"ngram\": \"a spectacular stage\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 368}, {\"ngram\": \"the July 26 ceremony\", \"from\": 373, \"to\": 393}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 402}, {\"ngram\": \"a 320,000-strong crowd\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge challenge\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 457}, {\"ngram\": \"security services\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"the safety\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 528}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 543}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French authorities said 45,000 police officers and gendarmes are being deployed for the occasion, as well as 10,000 soldiers of the so-called Sentinelle military operation.\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 552, \"end\": 558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Army\", \"score\": 0.9800564254810422, \"rank\": 0.01663461971863421, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Army\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Army\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"45,000 police officers\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 598}, {\"ngram\": \"gendarmes\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 612}, {\"ngram\": \"the occasion\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 648}, {\"ngram\": \"the so-called Sentinelle military operation\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A specially created battalion has been tasked to secure the embarkation zone for athletes located along Paris' eastern portion of the river.\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 830, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.637658407104417e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A specially created battalion\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 755}, {\"ngram\": \"the embarkation zone\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 815}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 865}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The battalion's mission includes the full protection of the area, the boats and the attendees, in close coordination with other security forces.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The battalion's mission\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 890}, {\"ngram\": \"the full protection\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 919}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 931}, {\"ngram\": \"the boats\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"the attendees\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 960}, {\"ngram\": \"close coordination\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"other security forces\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This mission is complex and unprecedented,\\\" Lieutenant-Colonel Olivier, chief of operations of the battalion, said Wednesday.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This mission\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1026}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\" Lieutenant-Colonel Olivier\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1084}, {\"ngram\": \"chief\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1091}, {\"ngram\": \"operations\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"the battalion\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1122}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's complex because we are in an environment - the Parisian environment, the Seine - which is an urban environment ... with obvious vulnerabilities.\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\