ris has been the target of deadly terror attacks in the past decade, and the Seine flows through the heart of the city, surrounded by office and apartment buildings and used every day by barges and other ships.\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1693, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1481, \"end\": 1486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.637658407104417e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1560, \"end\": 1565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8695638126355746e-16, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the target\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1506}, {\"ngram\": \"deadly terror attacks\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1531}, {\"ngram\": \"the past decade\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1589}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1601}, {\"ngram\": \"office and apartment buildings\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"barges\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1676}, {\"ngram\": \"other ships\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1692}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were already on a very high level of security.\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1745, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very high level\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1732}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So the attack on Donald Trump only reinforces our vigilance,\\\" Olivier said.\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1763, \"end\": 1775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9886730097785191, \"rank\": 0.011456710424771362, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the attack\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1759}, {\"ngram\": \"our vigilance\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"Olivier\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Military officers requested to be identified by their first names only for reasons of security.\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1918, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Military officers\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1840}, {\"ngram\": \"their first names\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1888}, {\"ngram\": \"reasons\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1917}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Specialized units have been mobilized for the operation that involves deployment of high-tech technology such as drones and sonars, as well as combat divers, boat intervention groups, patrols along the Seine and military dogs.\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 2146, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2122, \"end\": 2127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8695638126355746e-16, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Specialized units\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"the operation\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1975}, {\"ngram\": \"deployment\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2000}, {\"ngram\": \"high-tech technology\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2024}, {\"ngram\": \"drones\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2039}, {\"ngram\": \"sonars\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"combat divers\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2076}, {\"ngram\": \"boat intervention groups\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2102}, {\"ngram\": \"patrols\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Water barriers going from the riverbed to the surface have been installed to prevent any intrusions into protected area.\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2267, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Water barriers\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"the riverbed\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2185}, {\"ngram\": \"the surface\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2200}, {\"ngram\": \"any intrusions\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2246}, {\"ngram\": \"protected area\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, the battalion is using counter-drone systems and works in close coordination with the French Air Force, which secures the Paris skies, the lieutenant-colonel said.\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2368, \"end\": 2384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Air_and_Space_Force\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.614181800475407e-35, \"text\": \"French Air Force\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Air_and_Space_Force\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Air_and_Space_Force\"}, {\"begin\": 2404, \"end\": 2409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.637658407104417e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2280}, {\"ngram\": \"the battalion\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2295}, {\"ngram\": \"counter-drone systems\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2326}, {\"ngram\": \"works\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2336}, {\"ngram\": \"close coordination\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"the lieutenant-colonel\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The military \\\"is ready to respond to any type of threat\\\" that may be underwater, on water, on land or in the air, said Captain Quentin, who is commanding a company of the 13th Demi-Brigade of the Foreign Legion.\", \"fro