 \"deterrence\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 2841, \"to\": 2847}, {\"ngram\": \"site\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2855}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A special anti-terrorism perimeter for the opening ceremony will start being implemented Thursday.\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A special anti-terrorism perimeter\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2902}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2907, \"to\": 2927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Protected areas along the Seine have a special legal status, making them off-limits to the unauthorized public.\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 3078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2993, \"end\": 2998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8695638126355746e-16, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Protected areas\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 2982}, {\"ngram\": \"a special legal status\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3026}, {\"ngram\": \"off-limits\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3050}, {\"ngram\": \"the unauthorized public\", \"from\": 3054, \"to\": 3077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Staff Sergeant Sofiane, from the 132nd Canine Infantry Regiment, said his 3-year-old dog, Stimo, is trained to detect intruders and would alert him by barking.\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3239, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3080, \"end\": 3094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Staff_sergeant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.27526303145069e-33, \"text\": \"Staff Sergeant\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Staff_sergeant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Staff_sergeant\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 132nd Canine Infantry Regiment\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3143}, {\"ngram\": \"his 3-year-old dog\", \"from\": 3150, \"to\": 3168}, {\"ngram\": \"Stimo\", \"from\": 3170, \"to\": 3175}, {\"ngram\": \"intruders\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In case of an intrusion the staff sergeant could order Stimo to attack and neutralize an intruder, either hitting the person with a very rigid muzzle or attacking without the muzzle.\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"case\", \"from\": 3244, \"to\": 3248}, {\"ngram\": \"an intrusion\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3264}, {\"ngram\": \"the staff sergeant\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3283}, {\"ngram\": \"Stimo\", \"from\": 3296, \"to\": 3301}, {\"ngram\": \"an intruder\", \"from\": 3327, \"to\": 3338}, {\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3365}, {\"ngram\": \"a very rigid muzzle\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3390}, {\"ngram\": \"the muzzle\", \"from\": 3412, \"to\": 3422}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With France soon to be in the world's spotlight, the Olympics security mission is a unique experience for the soldiers, and even a chance for some to discover Paris.\", \"from\": 3425, \"to\": 3590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3430, \"end\": 3436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_France\", \"score\": 0.7761732868496644, \"rank\": 0.19769338687271584, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 3584, \"end\": 3589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.637658407104417e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world's spotlight\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3472}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics security mission\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3503}, {\"ngram\": \"a unique experience\", \"from\": 3507, \"to\": 3526}, {\"ngram\": \"the soldiers\", \"from\": 3531, \"to\": 3543}, {\"ngram\": \"even a chance\", \"from\": 3549, \"to\": 3562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They have the feeling that they are there for something special,\\\" Quentin said.\", \"from\": 3592, \"to\": 3672, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the feeling\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3614}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3639, \"to\": 3648}, {\"ngram\": \"Quentin\", \"from\": 3659, \"to\": 3666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And they are all the more vigilant and ready for the occasion.\\\"\", \"from\": 3673, \"to\": 3737, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the occasion\", \"from\": 3723, \"to\": 3735}]}]}"